Qd6 $1 $11 {This is the goal position for black} (16... O-O $6 {Is not so good
here because of the:} 17. Nf3 $1 Nxf3 18. Rxf3 e5 19. Rc4 Qb2 20. Rb3 Qxa2 21.
Ra4 {1-0 Campos Moreno,J (2480)-Martin Gonzalez,A (2445)/Barcelona 1991/CBM
023 ext}) (16... Bd7 $6 17. Rb3 {White regains the pawn and keep the
initiative. Mamedyarov,S (2503)-Kolev,A (2571) Leon 2001}) 17. Rb3 (17. Qd2 {
is too slow} Bd7 18. Kg1 Rd8 19. Qb2 Ba4 20. Nf3 Bc6 $15 {Black is better in
the game: Degtiarev,E (2374)-Naumann,A (2258) Caleta 2010}) (17. Rc2 {This
