a4 (18. f4 {just make some weaknesses in White's camp} Ng6 19. g3 Bb7 20. Rd3
Qb6 21. Bf3 Rd8 $15 {White has no compensation for the sacrificing material.})
18... bxa4 19. Rbc3 Bd7 20. h5 Rd8 $1 $146 (20... Rb8 21. f4 $1 Ng6 22. hxg6
hxg6 23. Qd2 Rh4 24. Kg1 Qxf4 $11 (24... Rxf4 {is also an interesting move
